DM_KILLFIELD_BETA

This map is a very fun, smaller deathmatch map with tons of cover. There is also a sniping balcony that wraps around the map for those AWP lovers, though i made it fair for the other players by not providing a lot of sniper cover. If you find any bugs or think something could be improved, please comment on this map or PM me.

Thank You,
[{GsH}] TheHuntzman
